    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "This Project seeks approval for an Additional Financing (AF) of a US$12 million grant from the PROGREEN Trust Fund to the Government of Nepal (GoN) for the ongoing “Forests for Prosperity” Project (FPP) (P170798). The proposed AF will cover a financing gap under Component 2 linked to community-based sustainable forest management and smallholder forest plantations. Furthermore, the project paper proposes a restructuring to improve the project design and introduce new activities that are fundamental to achieving the adjusted project’s outcomes. The restructuring will also reallocate financing across components and, thus, scale up Component 3 on forest enterprise development and improvement."
      },
